songs.title: Has To Be 1
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Breathe in, breathe out
I say a little prayer
How the gods above
Could be so unfair

[Verse 1]
I'm not so good when I'm alone
I don't like what I see
I never measure up to what
The world would like to think of me

[Chorus]
I know there's someone out there
Waiting for me
There must be someone out there
There just has to be

[Verse 2]
Go on, go on
Don't sit there like a fool
You've graduated from
A different kind of school

[Verse 3]
I should be glad that I'm alive
It could have been much worse
I might have never loved at all
And never known what I am worth
How the gods above
Could be so unfair


[Chorus]
I know there's someone out there
Waiting for me
There must be someone out there
There just has to be
I know there's someone out there
Waiting for me
There must be someone out there
There just has to be

[Intro]
Breathe in, breathe out
I say a little prayer
How the gods above
Could be so unfair

[Verse 3]
I'll just be glad that I'm alive
It could have been much worse
